<view class='page'>
  <view class='session' >
    <view class='title'>使用须知</view>
    <view class='text'> 第一次参与的受试者填写量表的时间不受任何时间限制，即无论是健康人、术前或术后的病人，均可以在任何时间参与到量表的填写；因数据有效期为4-8天，所以一旦参加到量表填写的受试者，填写完第一次的八天后，若受试者仍未能完成量表的填写，则数据失效；若八天过后，受试者者未能在规定时间内及时完成第二次的量表填写，则八天以后的再次填写算第一次填写</view>
  </view>
  <view class='session'>

    <view class="weui-flex weui-cells__title">
      <view class="weui-flex__item" style='width:50%;display:inline'>
        <view class="placeholder title " style='text-align:center;padding-bottom:20rpx; border-bottom:{{!open ? "":"1px solid #1aad19"}};color:{{!open ? "":"#1aad19"}}' bindtap='open'>开始测试</view>
      </view>
      <view class="weui-flex__item" style='width:50%;display:inline'>
        <view class="placeholder  title" style='text-align:center;padding-bottom:20rpx;  border-bottom:{{open ? "":"1px solid #1aad19"}};color:{{open ? "":"#1aad19"}}' bindtap='close'>历史记录</view>
    </view></view>

    <view class="weui-cells weui-cells_after-title"style='margin-top:10rpx'>
      <view wx:if="{{open}}">
        <view wx:for="{{name}}" bindtap='startTest' class='weui-cell'>
          <view id='{{index}}' class='weui-cell__bd'> {{item}}</view>
          <view class="weui-cell__ft weui-cell__ft_in-access"></view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view wx:else style='height:250rpx;'>
      <view bindtap='history' class='weui-cell'>
        <view id='{{index}}' class='weui-cell__bd'> 查看记录</view>
          <view class="weui-cell__ft weui-cell__ft_in-access"></view>
      </view></view>
    </view>

  </view>
</view>